Redesign `BriefingPanel.tsx` from its current flat layout into a four-section color-coded card layout matching the UX spec. Add Done/Snooze/Chat inline actions on priority items, display the NLP summary already stored in `morningBriefing.content.summary`, and wire Chat via a new `openChatWithContext` store action. **No backend changes needed** — all data already exists in the store.

